ctical optimization choices for using alternating\nminimization for induced DLMs, for both batch and stochastic gradient descent.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 17 Apr 2016 23:46:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Oct 2016 01:13:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 19 Feb 2017 16:10:17 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 7 Aug 2017 02:04:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-08"}
