approximable by polynomials uniformly on\nthe spectrahedron. These theorems are needed for classifying free bianalytic\nmaps.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Apr 2016 01:26:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 27 Aug 2016 00:09:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 31 Oct 2017 19:35:59 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 6 Dec 2018 20:48:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-10"}
