imulation results\ndemonstrate that the proposed scheme outperforms its counterpart, and it can\napproach the performance bound.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Apr 2016 02:46:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 23 Apr 2016 11:13:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-17"}
