y assumption, are strictly valid for the modes for which one can ignore\nthe radial variations in the density and the magnetic field profiles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Apr 2016 03:40:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-26"}
